item.description:
@aaronmead wrote:

Whatever the code is like E.G “Welcome to RuneScape” and you want it to be changed to such as … “DannScape”
then go to actionsender.java, and search for “Welcome to RuneScape” and change it to “Welcome to DannScape”. If it fixes some but some lines are still the same ~ search your source for “Authentication.py” and it should be in that file too.
